text: Bought a burger at this Cheers and it was missing a lettuce + the patty was half the size of the image.

Prices are double the price at usual supermarket. $2 for the usual Fairprice chips which usually is priced at $1, $5 for a 1.5L drinking water! Closing time stated to be 8pm but at 7pm the staff said they closing soon and keep rushing us to make the last purchase. Doors locked at 7.15pm..

Small convenience shop amongst the restaurants near Bird Paradise. A top tip is if you havenâ€™t brought any snacks or drinks to Bird Paradise, you should buy them from this shop before entering into the park as the prices here are much lower than inside.
The timing say to 6, now 5.28pm already close?
4 dollars for a small bottle of Gatorade, the least you could do is make sure your fridge chills the drinks.
